metadata.name: Blue Leaves Textile Pattern
metadata.description:
This tileable textile pattern consists of a collection of leaves in a blue hue with different brightness and saturation. It is meant to be printed on fabric.

The pattern is saved as a PNG image with a resolution of 4096 px x 4096 px and a file size of 10,7 MB. The image can be tiled seamlessly, as needed.

The textile pattern was created by Jes Fink-Jensen with the help of Stable Diffusion AI.
